mpd2mpris (0.12.0~beta.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rename project mpDris2 -> mpd2mpris (in agreement with the original
    maintainer) to avoid confusion with eonpatapon/mpDris2.
  * Source and binary package renamed mpdris2 -> mpd2mpris; the binary,
    systemd unit and config dir follow (Conflicts/Replaces/Provides:
    mpdris2 for a clean upgrade). The MPRIS bus name
    org.mpris.MediaPlayer2.mpd is unchanged.

